| Section | Image Ratio | Mobile Technique | Container Key CSS |
|---------|-------------|-----------------|-------------------|
| 1 (Kerala) | 5:6 portrait | `object-contain` + `max-height: 22vh` + dark bg | `background: #1a0a2e` blends side bars |
